44f","tid":130320,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803fdff793bbb8d53be5dbf763b55773c0620abc","tid":130320,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/224839_7a968264519602df84f686fe30da4d37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F224839_7a968264519602df84f686fe30da4d37.jpg&h=f9c35669&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/224840_b09b3d80142f993ff3253369fd551c1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F224840_b09b3d80142f993ff3253369fd551c1d.jpg&h=12cba911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\njeng"},{"pid":"8c3c68c0839aff7605e86ff82c10d9f1b368ae26","tid":130320,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:50:44.000Z","msg":"kuah都有間wonderland seafood, 不過冇真浪咁正, 唔近酒店唔洗去"},{"pid":"008da603a1421496850588693c474906de75a74b","tid":130320,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>kuah都有間wonderland seafood, 不過冇真浪咁正, 唔近酒店唔洗去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真浪我有 bookmark 咗，<br />\n呢間遠我間 resort, 仲 mark 咗幾間，可能全部都試下。<br />\n<br />\nThanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721c0cfa62a6689c9d7f9441bc497fe937377cf7","tid":130320,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T16:10:40.000Z","msg":"巴打自駕遊？"},{"pid":"4895a28569b0311c8163de20930db7107f01d6fc","tid":130320,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:18:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打自駕遊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係，所以一定搵 resort 附近食。<br />\n<br />\n住珍南"},{"pid":"65f94fe681aaf27d9f6e9c3aa88c9299f90ec9a5","tid":130320,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打自駕遊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係，所以一定搵 resort 附近食。<br />\n<br />\n住珍南</blockquote><br />\n咁一定要食附近，條街完全冇的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n珍南大把，成條街都係"},{"pid":"73a369a70266617c61b1648c86ca8a56d9710c06","tid":130320,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:02:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5e1d799a6950802ae7a033b4a8ec777cbe25a57","tid":130320,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:03:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14e388bb781004b12217f9a54c3c5c81822095fc","tid":130320,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:30:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打自駕遊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係，所以一定搵 resort 附近食。<br />\n<br />\n住珍南</blockquote><br />\n咁一定要食附近，條街完全冇的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n珍南大把，成條街都係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一早做定功課睇到呢幾間，啲人都講到OK，諗着食足咁多餐，間間試勻晒。<br />\n<br />\n卓峰海鮮餐廳<br />\n燈籠海鮮餐館<br />\n強師傅海鮮飯店<br />\n真浪花園海鮮餐廳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過睇下連登仔有無其他好提議。<br />\n<br />\n出完機票先知呢度原來無巴士，出入都靠的士，依家淨係諗住出入機場先會坐的士，跟着咁多日都在珍南算。<br />\n<br />\n不過咁仲好，乜功課都唔洗做，因為邊度都唔會去。"},{"pid":"8053161f626be59c166a983e77ef8d6be1eba2f1","tid":130320,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f63d43c1ab3c6c8f9119c631551d052eaf7006","tid":130320,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:18:25.000Z","msg":"抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234f87e704beb0a1caf56ded1ae0369302b2e030","tid":130320,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T13:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote